short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Click and call from web page!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension is developed to integrate the Softphone.Pro with web site:
 - Click to Call dialing from any web pages
 - Click to Call dialing from any CRM or HelpDesk 
 - Click to Call from Google Sheets
 - Click to Call from Google Doc

Perfectly works if you need to make outbound call campaign with Google Sheets.
